 />\n佢家姐搵個靚仔損精生個俾佢就攪掂<br />\n而加呢2個真係同佢冇關係<br />\n輕鬆留返俾細佬對住2個女打飛機"},{"pid":"eb79d379d63f3ef6de577bcbb8db24517f93332f","tid":2507571,"uid":187153,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:01:58.000Z","msg":"難怪細佬一直窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來两個女由家姐養咪仲好<br />\n反正邊個養都係生父<br />\n無錢仲要養多两件，又無家姐接濟"},{"pid":"9713689a84bdf5fc8e5e8030bce64d076890968d","tid":2507571,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:02:53.000Z","msg":"成家人都on9<br />\n個家姐唔想結婚 要搵代孕？<br />\n你自己生唔撚到咩 唔結婚都可以生呀 應該係痛恨男人果種痴線老姑婆<br />\n<br />\n個細佬就仆街 只係想要錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff660d60704877bda00942330cae76ffa54791a","tid":2507571,"uid":10125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9713689a84bdf5fc8e5e8030bce64d076890968d","tid":2507571,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:02:53.000Z","msg":"成家人都on9<br />\n個家姐唔想結婚 要搵代孕？<br />\n你自己生唔撚到咩 唔結婚都可以生呀 應該係痛恨男人果種痴線老姑婆<br />\n<br />\n個細佬就仆街 只係想要錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:12:45.000Z","msg":"50歲啵...? 唔搵代孕點生...?"},{"pid":"77ae1238f15e629b501299b6a3fd8270c2c92eae","tid":2507571,"uid":76674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ea70d203e5da364e1d6f89e5561e0e28da7167d","tid":2507571,"uid":137569,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:02:56.000Z","msg":"個細佬on9<br />\n家姐無家庭<br />\n將來咪又分番份俾你<br />\n依家無啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T07:26:58.000Z","msg":"醒既唔會做擔泥啦"}]}